---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---
<BaseLayout
  title="VPlus Device Leasing — Preconfigured Android Devices for Ops"
  description="Lease Android devices preloaded with VPick+, VPlus, or VPlus Lite. Bluetooth scanner support, updates, and 36-month refresh cycles."
>
  <nav class="breadcrumb container" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
    <a href="/">Home</a>
    <span class="separator">›</span>
    <span aria-current="page">Device Leasing</span>
  </nav>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container hero-wrap">
      <div class="hero-copy">
        <h1>VPlus Device Leasing</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          Preconfigured Android devices, refreshed every 36 months. Reduce CAPEX, accelerate deployment, and keep costs predictable.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-cta">
          <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="mailto:info@vpickplus.us?subject=VPlus%20Device%20Leasing%20Quote%20Request">Request a Leasing Quote</a>
        </div>
        <p class="muted" style="margin-top:10px;">Bundles available for VPlus Lite, VPlus, and VPick+. Bluetooth scanners supported.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-image">
        <img src="/assets/hero/generic-android-device.png" alt="Preconfigured Android device for warehouse use" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="alt">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>How it works</h2>
      <ol class="steps">
        <li><div><strong>Select a bundle:</strong> Devices ship ready for VPlus Lite, VPlus, or VPick+. Scanners and accessories are optional add-ons.</div></li>
        <li><div><strong>We provision:</strong> MDM enrollment, Wi-Fi profiles, and app configuration.</div></li>
        <li><div><strong>We ship:</strong> Devices arrive ready for pair-and-go with Bluetooth scanners.</div></li>
        <li><div><strong>Operate:</strong> OS &amp; app updates, and RMA support under your selected SLA.</div></li>
        <li><div><strong>Refresh:</strong> Seamless device refresh at 36 months (or retire/return).</div></li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Bundles</h2>
      <div class="grid-3" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
        <article class="card hover-lift">
          <h3>VPlus Lite</h3>
          <p>Lightweight UI for simple workflows (<strong>no voice</strong>).</p>
          <ul class="list">
            <li>Android device (<em>no scanner included</em>)</li>
            <li>Supports Bluetooth scanners</li>
            <li>Ideal for basic pick/put workflows</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
        <article class="card hover-lift">
          <h3>VPlus</h3>
          <p>Programmable UI (<strong>no voice</strong>), richer UX and integrations.</p>
          <ul class="list">
            <li>Android device (<em>no scanner included</em>)</li>
            <li>Supports Bluetooth scanners</li>
            <li>Advanced screens &amp; workflow customization</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
        <article class="card hover-lift">
          <h3>VPick+</h3>
          <p>Voice + screen + scan with <em>SilentScan™</em>.</p>
          <ul class="list">
            <li>Android device (<em>no scanner included</em>)</li>
            <li>Supports Bluetooth scanners</li>
            <li>Warehouse headset available as an add-on</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="alt">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>What's included</h2>
      <ul class="checklist">
        <li>Android device provisioning (MDM enrollment, Wi-Fi profiles, configuration)</li>
        <li>OS &amp; app updates during the lease term</li>
        <li>RMA handling with defined SLAs; optional advance replacement</li>
        <li>Device refresh or retire at 36-month term end</li>
        <li><strong>Note:</strong> Scanners and accessories are not included and may be leased separately or supplied by customer.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>SLA tiers</h2>
      <div class="grid-3" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
        <article class="card"><h3>Standard</h3><p>3–5 day RMA</p></article>
        <article class="card"><h3>Priority</h3><p>2–3 day RMA</p></article>
        <article class="card"><h3>Premium</h3><p>NBD advance replacement</p></article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Optional add-ons</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Accessories typically outlast devices, so they're not bundled by default.</p>
      <div class="grid-2" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
        <article class="card">
          <h3>Bluetooth scanners</h3>
          <p>Pair with any leased device. Lease from us or bring your own.</p>
          <ul class="list">
            <li>Low power draw</li>
            <li>Long lifespan vs devices</li>
            <li>Ideal for high-velocity workflows</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h3>Accessories</h3>
          <ul class="list">
            <li>Warehouse headsets</li>
            <li>Belt slings &amp; holsters</li>
            <li>Protective cases</li>
            <li>Charging cradles &amp; mounts</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-band">
    <div class="container cta-band-inner">
      <p><strong>Ready for predictable OPEX?</strong></p>
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="mailto:info@vpickplus.us?subject=VPlus%20Device%20Leasing%20Quote%20Request">Request a Leasing Quote</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
